        <title>main:modding_docs:explosions</title>
        <link>http://gusanos.sourceforge.net/documentation/doku/doku.php?id=main:modding_docs:explosions&amp;rev=1316364402&amp;do=diff</link>
        <description>These properties may only be used in explosions; .exp files.

alpha
alpha = &lt;int&gt; ( from 0 to 255 )
Alpha is the value of transparency used by the blender. This cannot be used without specifying the blender.

Default value: 255

anim_type
anim_type = { ping_pong / loop_right / right_once }
Determines the behaviour of the sprite animation. See also Anim_Types.</description>
    </item>
